title: Activator (Crack) for Windows Vista Ultimate (and others) 32bit
description:
Fully automatic so simply double click on the file.


Please note: This is not a time stopper. Activates Vista fully.



It will install the appropriate Product Key for your version of Vista.

It will install a license thus fully activating Windows Vista.

Friendly on screen prompts, although a successful installation will only prompt once to inform you of the success and ask that you restart.


Supports Microsoft Windows Vista (X86)(32Bit):

Ultimate
Business
Home Basic
Home Premium

Also supports Service Pack 1.

This activator does not always require a clean install of Vista and has been tested to work after Vista being fully updated from Microsoft whilst in it's 30 days trial period and activation was still sucessful.

Your Windows Vista will be fully updatable from Microsoft.

I have coded this programme myself so I know for a fact it is virus free.
